articles.description: Vladimir Brodziansky scored 25 points, Kouat Noi had his second straight career high with 18 and TCU won an important matchup between teams battling for the NCAA Tournament, beating Texas 87-71 on Saturday.
articles.headline: TCU cruises past Texas 87-71 in matchup of NCAA hopefuls

articles.description: Shawn Anderson and Evan Weick scored 16 of their combined 25 points in the second half and Tom Lacey finished with 10 points and nine rebounds to help Navy beat Army 68-59 on Saturday.
articles.headline: Navy leads wire-to-wire in 68-59 win over Army

articles.description: Luke Maye scored 27 of his career-high 33 points after halftime to help No. 21 North Carolina beat rival North Carolina State 96-89 on Saturday.
articles.headline: Maye helps No. 21 North Carolina beat rival NC State 96-89

images.caption: Luke Maye drains a quick 3 en route to scoring 11 of North Carolina's first 15 points coming out of the break.
images.name: Maye opens up 2nd half with hot hand

articles.description: Solomon Young leaps to deflect the ball and gets it to Lindell Wigginton who hits a quick 3-pointer to put the Cyclones up 6.
articles.headline: Wigginton buries 3 for Iowa State

images.caption: Solomon Young leaps to deflect the ball and gets it to Lindell Wigginton who hits a quick 3-pointer to put the Cyclones up 6.
images.name: Solomon Young leaps to deflect the ball and gets it to Lindell Wigginton who hits a quick 3-pointer to put the Cyclones up 6.

articles.description: Baylor's Manu Lecomte sinks two 3-pointers from the logo late to put the Bears up by 10.
articles.headline: Lecomte rains back-to-back 3s over KU

images.caption: Baylor's Manu Lecomte sinks two 3-pointers from the logo late to put the Bears up by 10.
